subject: Automobile Racing
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Danica Patrick, known for her GoDaddy.com Super Bowl commercials as well as for her racing, has become the show at the Daytona 500 after winning the pole.
